    {
      "title": "Substitute x = 2 into the function",
      "content": "We need to find $f(2)$ where $f(x) = 9x^3 + 8$. Substitute $x = 2$:<br/><br/>$$f(2) = 9(2)^3 + 8$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Simplify the expression",
      "content": "Evaluate $(2)^3 = 8$:<br/><br/>$$f(2) = 9 \\cdot 8 + 8$$<br/><br/>Multiply: $9 \\cdot 8 = 72$<br/><br/>$$f(2) = 72 + 8 = 80$$<br/><br/>The answer is 80."
    }
  ]
}